title: People's Court: He Does Half of a Chore
description: E White is being taken to court by his girlfriend Elise for only doing half of a chore when he does it.  For example, he'll put dishes in the dishwasher but he won't wash the pots and pans that don't go in the dishwasher.    Is E White guilty?
